# Resolving the pamac don't start problem
# Error message: Process org.manjaro.pamac.manager exited with status 127

# Solution: remove pamac-all & reinstall pamac-gtk
# How to ?

1/ sudo pacman -R pamac-all
2/ sudo pacman -R libpamac-full
3/ sudo pacman -R archlinux-appstream-data-pamac
4/ yay pamac then choose pamac-gtk, it will install
                                         archlinux-appstream-data-pamac
                                         libpamac
                                         pamac-cli
                                         pamac-gtk

                                         The job is done.

